title: Fighting American - Awesome Entertainment.rar
description:
This is the character that was revived by Awesome Entertainment when they acquired the right to the character from Simon and Kirby. Good stories from Jeph Loeb, so if you're turned off thinking it's just a lousy Captain America rip-off, don't be too hasty: it's actually a pretty decent Captain America rip-off.

Also, if this is of any interest to you at all I'd recommend Alan Moore's "Supreme" stuff from Awesome Entertainment too.

Enjoy
